Nam nec ille se in vulgus eduxit, ne impii errore liberarentur, ut et 10 fides, non mediocri praemio destinata, difficultate constaret. 5. custodia pavore disjecta. Disjieere is the regular military term for routing and dispersing a guard of soldiery ; comp. Hor. Epp. ii. 2. 303 Liv. xliv. 41. Dejicere occurs in the same sense ch. 27, like depellere, ch. 9, 24, 37.
